This directory contains the penguin tower a GNU Modula-2 testcase.

This software is part of the GNU Modula-2 project, as a test application
which stresses the PIM coroutines library.  All the code is covered by the
GNU Public License - see COPYING for details.

Please see doc/penguin-tower.info, doc/ptower.texi, doc/ptower.html or
doc/ptower.pdf for details about this package.
